Class PsnUser

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.krobothsoftware.snc.sen.psn.us.model.PsnUser
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    OnlineId, Serializable

    public class PsnUser
extends Object
implements OnlineId, Serializable
    Holds all personal Info in an US account. Not all data here will be filled, depends on account. Relies on cookie userinfo.
